q_en: Which cutting tasks have been completed by Master Cutters?

steps.sql: SELECT id FROM working_group WHERE name = 'Master Cutters';
steps.description: Retrieve the working group ID for the group named "Master Cutters"

steps.sql: SELECT id, start_time, end_time, planned_number, completed_number FROM cutting_tasks WHERE working_group_id = '3' AND status = 2;
steps.description: Retrieve the cutting tasks that have been completed by the working group "Master Cutters"
